- Capabilities approach: 4 papers - Housing justice as enabling functionings and capabilities (Kimhur, Dummer & Neuh\u00e4user, Taylor)
- Applied analyses: 5 papers - Specific housing issues through justice lens (gentrification, limitarianism, allocation)
